title: Order, chaos icons
body:
Hey, is it too late to get the Chaos/Order icons? because I started playing again a week ago and I didn't recieve them, 
was wondering if I missed it.
Thanks!

replies.body: Since the [**VS Event ended on 6/29/2017**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/events/vs-2017) you can no longer get tokens since the missions that dropped them are over. Missions will be returning at some point in the future so be sure to check out the [**news page**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news) for that info!
